snippet.title: Project GingerSnap - Gameplay Clip 1
snippet.description:
Thinking about posting little clips of gameplay here and there to show off some features, idk. Show I'm still working on this thing.

Here are some abilities and a little bit of what I'm calling "chain dashing," where if you dash again *right* before your dash ends, you're granted a longer, faster dash. This can be done repeatedly for exponential increases. No limit on it either so it can get pretty wild, might make speedruns interesting.
